    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It starts and runs flawlessly, with no mechanical issues to note. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, or paint imperfections, and the interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 everything is clean and fully functional. This vehicle has been exceptionally well maintained and is ready for immediate use.",
